## Filtering logs

By default, every log record triggers the function. The optional `filter` property lets you narrow which records cause an invocation.

...
// [!code focus-start]
export default defineConfig(() => {
  const errorMonitor = new LambdaFunction({
    ...
    events: [
      new CloudwatchLogIntegration({
        logGroupArn: 'arn:aws:logs:eu-west-1:123456789012:log-group:/aws/lambda/my-app:*',
        filter: '{ $.level = "error" }'
      })
    ]

